== Rosettacode is NOT a blogging site ==

Rosettacode is NOT a blogging site. Rosettacode is NOT a social media site. You were asked to curb your excesses. You did not. You have been curbed. If you invested one twentieth of the effort into contributing to the site as you did to stroking your ego, I would be more inclined to overlook it.

Using things in a unique way outside their intended purpose even after you have been asked to stop is often perceived as being a narcissistic git. Next time there will be some banning involved. --[[User:Thundergnat|Thundergnat]] ([[User talk:Thundergnat|talk]]) 10:24, 14 July 2019 (UTC)
